    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for platform-specific input adapters. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a unified interface for querying input device states across different platforms. Concrete implementations translate generic input queries into platform-specific API calls.</para>
<para>The adapter manages per-gamepad configuration through `GamepadSettings` and applies input normalization via a configurable `DeadzoneStrategy`.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>GLFWInputAdapter for a GLFW-based implementation. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>GamepadSettings for per-controller configuration options. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>DeadzoneStrategy for <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1input" kindref="compound">input</ref> normalization strategies. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
